rdf:Description.Label: Based on the selected host site included in the deployment plan, what are the interfaces and modernization activities?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: TAP_Site_Data&FutureDB& SELECT DISTINCT ?HostSite ?System WHERE { BIND(<@DCSite-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/DCSite@> AS ?HostSite) {?DCSite <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/DCSite>} {?SystemDCSite <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemDCSite>} {?SystemDCSite <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/DeployedAt> ?HostSite}{?Wave <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/Wave>}{?Wave <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains> ?HostSite} {?System <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/System>} {?System <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/DeployedAt> ?SystemDCSite} } ORDER BY ?HostSite ?System & SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?OtherSystem ?Interface ?ModernizationActivity WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?OtherSystem ?Interface ?ModernizationActivity WHERE { {?Interface <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ProposedDecommissionedInterfaceControlDocument> ;} BIND('Propose to Decommission' AS ?ModernizationActivity) { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Interface ?OtherSystem WHERE { {?System <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide> ?Interface ;} {?Interface <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consume> ?OtherSystem} } } UNION { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Interface ?OtherSystem WHERE { {?Interface <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consume> ?System} {?OtherSystem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide> ?Interface} } } } } UNION { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Interface ?OtherSystem ?ModernizationActivity WHERE { {?Interface <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ProposedInterfaceControlDocument> ;} BIND('Propose to Create' AS ?ModernizationActivity) { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?OtherSystem ?Interface WHERE { {?System <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide> ?Interface} {?Interface <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consume> ?OtherSystem} } } UNION { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?OtherSystem ?Interface WHERE { {?Interface <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consume> ?System ;} {?OtherSystem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide> ?Interface} } } } } }&false&false
